Title: Wanted: Fenistrasza's Skull
Description:
<The posted sign is written in beautiful calligraphy.>

The archivists humbly request that all expedition members seek out Fenistrasza's Skull for our artifact archives.

If acquired, please deliver to Cataloger Jakes for processing and compensation.

Some expedition members have reported seeing it in the possession of an outcast djaradin in the western mountains, but no one has been able to convince him to part with it yet.
PortraitGiverText: A reclusive djaradin keeps the enchanted skull on display in his alcove.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Cataloger Jakes in the Dragonscale Basecamp.
